Author: MidoriKami
Name: DailyDuty
Punchline: Easily Track Daily and Weekly tasks.
Description: Automatically track and complete many daily and weekly tasks.
Changelog:
Major Version Jump! Big new features.

Doman Enclave, and Custom Delivery now use internal game data for tracking!
Values will be correct even if the plugin was disabled for a few days as you completed tasks.

The Doman Enclave module requires visiting the enclave ***once*** to get initialized properly (per character).

Added Super Secret Special things that will be around for the start of next month ;)

Misc Changes:
Fixed: No Clickthrough not actually being no clickthrough and blocking user input
Fixed: Display message in timers window when no timers are enabled
Fixed: Typo in Leviquest module. **This will reset your Leviquest settings**
Added: Commands to show and hide todo and timers window `/dd todo` and `/dd timers` respectively
